Provides: noctalia-shell
Description: Sleek Wayland desktop shell (v5 alpha)
 Noctalia v5 is a complete C++ rewrite of the popular desktop shell,
 built directly on Wayland and OpenGL ES with cairo/pango rendering.
 It provides bars, panels, notifications, a dock, lock screen,
 wallpapers, OSD, and nearly 100 plugins — without pulling in Qt6.
 .
 Native support for Niri, Hyprland, Sway, Scroll, Labwc, and MangoWC.
 This package is compiled from the latest v5 branch source with
 optimizations for x86-64-v3.
 .
 Note: This is alpha software. Expect rough edges.
